definitions.definition: To show or watch something, or part of it, before it is complete.
To show something in advance, a facility for viewing and checking a document or photo, or changes to it, before saving or printing it.

main_definition: ( transitive ) To show or watch something, or part of it, before it is complete.
secondary_definitions: ( computing , transitive ) To show something in advance, a facility for viewing and checking a document or photo, or changes to it, before saving or printing it.
